---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Festina Lente">
  <main class="landing">

    <div class="wordmark fade-in">FL</div>

    <div class="hero-block">
      <h1 class="phrase fade-in fade-in-delay-1">Festina<br /><em>Lente</em></h1>
      <p class="definition fade-in fade-in-delay-2">
        <em>Latin.</em> &ldquo;Make haste slowly.&rdquo;
      </p>
      <span class="rule fade-in fade-in-delay-3"></span>
    </div>

    <div class="origin fade-in fade-in-delay-3">
      <p>
        The phrase was a personal maxim of the Emperor Augustus, who believed that
        the surest path to lasting achievement was disciplined, unhurried deliberation —
        not the absence of urgency, but its careful direction.
      </p>
      <p>
        In the Renaissance, the Venetian printer Aldus Manutius adopted it as his
        device: an anchor entwined with a dolphin — anchored to purpose, swift in
        execution. It became the mark of work built to endure.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mission fade-in fade-in-delay-4">
      <p class="mission-label">What we&rsquo;re building</p>
      <p class="mission-text">
        The legal system moves on language, precedent, and argument.
        We&rsquo;re building AI tools that help legal professionals do all three
        with greater precision, speed, and confidence — without cutting corners.
      </p>
      <p class="mission-text">
        More soon. Built carefully.
      </p>
      <a href="mailto:hello@festinalente.ai" class="cta">
        hello@festinalente.ai <span class="arrow">&#8594;</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <footer class="landing-footer fade-in">
      <span class="anchor-dolphin" title="Anchor &amp; Dolphin — Aldus Manutius">&#9875;</span>
      <p>&copy; 2025 Festina Lente. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .landing {
    min-height: 100vh;
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 6rem 2rem 4rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4rem;
  }

  /* Fade-in animation (mirrors the global one for this standalone page) */
  .fade-in {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(20px);
    animation: fadeUp 0.9s ease forwards;
  }
  .fade-in-delay-1 { animation-delay: 0.15s; }
  .fade-in-delay-2 { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
  .fade-in-delay-3 { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
  .fade-in-delay-4 { animation-delay: 0.75s; }
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  .wordmark {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  .hero-block { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }

  .phrase {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(4rem, 12vw, 8rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.0;
    color: var(--cream);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .phrase em { font-style: italic; color: var(--gold-light); }

  .definition {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .definition em {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--cream);
    font-size: 1.05em;
  }

  .rule {
    display: block;
    width: 48px;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--gold);
  }

  .origin {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    border-left: 2px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2);
    padding-left: 1.75rem;
  }
  .origin p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: rgba(245,240,232,0.65);
  }

  .mission { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; }
  .mission-label {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
  .mission-text {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: rgba(245,240,232,0.8);
  }

  .cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.3);
    padding-bottom: 0.2rem;
    width: fit-content;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }
  .cta:hover { color: var(--cream); }
  .arrow { transition: transform 0.2s ease; }
  .cta:hover .arrow { transform: translateX(4px); }

  .landing-footer {
    margin-top: auto;
    padding-top: 3rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.1);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  .anchor-dolphin { font-size: 1.4rem; opacity: 0.4; }
  .landing-footer p {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    opacity: 0.5;
  }
</style>
